description:
Dakota Norths been kidnapped by members of The Untouchables, and only Cage and Punisher have the intel to save her. But will Cages worst shakedown of Hardcore be enough?

Dakota is kidnapped by Kickback, Tombstone, Hardcore and Nitro. Cage must team-up with the Punisher.
name: Second Chances

description: Cage in Colorado! Picking up a job for Troop, Cage and Micky travel to the American West to locate a missing guardian. A sinister state trooper is much more than he seems.
name: The Evil and the Cure, Part 1 of 4: Survival of the baddest!

description: Luke Cage has an unwelcome blast from the past while imprisoned at a facility thats experimenting with the Power Man serum! Innocent civilians are put through inhumane testing. Will a new generation of impenetrable Power Men and Women see the light of day? Not if Cage can help it!
name: The Evil and the Cure, Part 2 of 4: Captain of Destiny

description: Free from his bonds at a corrupt laboratory, Luke Cage hunts down Hardcore to have him answer for his misdeeds! A super-powered struggle in the mighty Marvel manner!
name: The Evil and the Cure, Part 3 of 4: The Power Principle

description: Stories converge and explode in this jam-packed issue! Dakota North gets closer to finding Lukes fatherbut is someone else tracking the same man? Meanwhile, Cage and the West Coast Avengers divert the disaster of the Power Man serum contaminating a local water supply!
name: The Evil and the Cure, Part 4 of 4: Signifying Nothing

description: Cage is in over his head when a client distorts the truth behind a case. Enter the Rhino, a villain as impenetrable as Cage!
name: Good Cop, Bad Cop

description: Two heavy-hitters, one single issue! The Hulk comes to town looking for the Rhinoand some answers. But will Luke Cage be able to talk sense into an animalistic Hulk? No chance.
name: Payback!

description: Cage set-up by Troop? But why? Former allies reveal their true colors, as a gang named Trash takes the villainous spotlight. What does Trash want with Cage?
name: Ganxtas

description:
Nothing will stop Cage in the pursuit of his brother and fathernot even Hardcore! Lukes closest relatives are being held hostage by this dangerous madman. Will Cage find the answers he needs before its too late?

An old enemy has kidnapped Luke's loved ones and put them in a death trap. Luke must rescue them all. Iron Fist shows up to help but Luke wants to pound him as well!
name: The Life and Death of Luke Cage
For Love nor Money part 2 of 6
For Love nor Money part 5 of 6

description: An Infinity Crusade crossover.
name: Luke Cage Killed His Mother!

description:
Original Series Numbering #451

The wait is over! Exactly what happened during Daredevils year-long reign as the new Kingpin?

His historic cleaning of Hells Kitchen will finally be revealed in bloody detail.

Framed around the Ten Commandments, this epic story-arc is like nothing youve seen before!
name: Decalogue, Part 1

description:
Original Series Numbering #452

Exactly how much was Matt Murdock willing to sacrifice in his obsession to clean up Hells Kitchen?

And what does it have to do with a painful family legacy?

The next episode exploring Daredevils year-long reign as the new Kingpin, framed around The Ten Commandments.
name: Decalogue, Part 2

description: Half-man, half-machine Deathlok is charged with recovering Nick Furys Infinity Formula. And if Deathlok should failit would spell certain death for Fury! The stakes have never been higher, as Marvels mighty cyborg takes on Leviathan for Nick Fury's life!
name: Infinity is Forever After All

description: Nick Fury and Alpha Flights Weapon Omega team-up to stop Ultimatum from wiping out the World Unity Council. A cruise goes horribly awry, as the worlds peacekeepers fall under attack by a terrorist cell! Plus, Nick Fury goes black-tie!
name: Formal Wear

description:
Its a brand new direction for S.H.I.E.L.D., as Nick Fury recruits a wave of superhero agents! Meet Ivory, Psi-Borg, Knockabout, and Violence!

The S.H.I.E.L.D. helicarrier comes under attack.
name: Man of Action

description:
Baron Strucker makes a power play that leaves Fury and his new agents reeling. The Super Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. vs. the deadly Balance of Terror!

The battle for the helicarrier rages on.
name: In The Field

description: Nick Fury and the agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. must defend the Helicarrier from complete take-over. Its a battle for the skies, as all havoc breaks loose on S.H.I.E.L.D.s flying base! Who are the villains behind this infiltration?
name: More Men of Action
The Snake Who Came In From The Cold
The Cold War of Nick Fury, Part 1: The Fourth Horseman
The Cold War of Nick Fury, Part 2: A Hunger For Freedom
The Cold War of Nick Fury, Part 3: Salvation
